Hydras:

Hydras growled with annoyance; Since his defeat, the escape of his Maximals 
prisioners and the destruction of the Blackfortess, he  wasnt very happy.
The predacon Leader looked around and frowned, his current quarters wasnt so 
confortable as his former ones, but he expect that this was a slight step 
back.

With the time this damaged place woud be repaired and become more fuctional 
and confortable too. Hydras looked the damaged walls of  the room, covered 
mostly with holes and leaks. Light blinked while the predacon leader walked 
towards the Main room, where Cyclonus were. The ship was showed diferent 
repair status.

The predacon leader opened his com link and said "Gather all PRedacons that 
are fully repared  where you are, I'm coming there"

It was time to do something, and do it now

CYCLONUS voice responded on the same frequency. �The ship is largely
repaired. It will not be worthy of flight just yet, but defenses,
sensors and weapons are largely online.�

There was a pause from CYCLONUS as if he were perhaps consulting
someone else, �The repairs to our personnel are also nearly done, only
our most damaged soldiers are still in the repair pods, and they
should be out soon.�

�Also.� CYCLONUS continued, his voice turning curious and surprised as
he spoke, �The reports from the battle scene we had discussed are
showing nothing. There are no bodies, no wreckage. The sweeps could
pick up residual energy reading from both Insectile as well as
Uniconrian sources, but nothing else. It is as if someone cleaned it
all up.�
